body:
Hi there! Not sure where to post this, but I was hoping to see if the [temporalio/web](https://hub.docker.com/r/temporalio/web/tags) docker hub image could get support for `arm64`? Most of the other images have this support already (e.g. `temporalio/auto-setup`), so just wanting to see if the `web` image can be brought up to parity.

Thanks!! üôè
title: Docker hub arm64 support for temporal/web image
